data.description: This spacious and secluded property, located on a dead-end road, offers 1.33 acres of mostly cleared land and surrounded by tall trees and a creek in the back of the property. With 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, it provides ample space for a comfortable living. The property boasts a new roof and a new porch. If you value serenity and peacefulness, this house is a must-see. House is being sold as-is.
